additional_house_rules:

* You are more than welcome to enjoy yourself, however no loud music and absolutely not any ilic activities are allowed! 

* If you have more people that you initially booked please inform me!

* I hope that you enjoy your New York stay and that you have a great memories and stories to tell :)
description:
- PRICE CHANGES AND ALL DEPENDS OF THE TIME OF THE YEAR. - NOW IS TIMETO BOOK ITS SUPER AFFORDABLE!!!

- YOU WILL SEE EXACT PRICING ONCE YOU CHOOSE YOUR DATES AND TOTAL NUMBER OF GUESTS!

- PLEASE READ GUEST ACCESS  IT'S LOCATED IN DESCRIPTION ;)

This is a 1 BA apartment located in the Heart of Manhattan in Time Square area. 
The apartment has a nice room with a queen size bed that can easily accommodate 2 guests and there is also a computer desk for your laptop! Addition to that room has a big closet space for your discretion! You will also have a full access to the living room with a comfy sofa bed! The bed can easily be adjusted into a queen size bed and can also accommodate 2 guests!
My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, families (with kids) and everyone in between :) 

YOU WILL EXPERIENCE AUTHENTIC NEW YORK LIFESTYLE. MY PLACE IS LOCATED ON A 3RD FLOOR OF A WALK UP BUILDING  THERE IS TOTAL OF 45 STEPS! 
ADITION TO THAT, MY PLACE IS LOCATED ON A BUSY STREET AND THERE IS ALSO A CONSTRICTION NEXT DOOR!   
IF YOU PREFER QUITE PLACE THIS MAY NOT BE THE FIT FOR YOU!!!! 
 MY PLACE IS VINTAGE !!! THERE ARE SOME MODERN STAFF  LIKE 50INCH TV AND AWESOME ROOF TOP :) 

IF YOU PREFER QUITE PLACE THIS APARTMENT MAY NOT BE THE BEST FIT FOR YOU!! 

ITS A GREAT PLACE FOR THE BUCK, SOME PRIVATE ROOMS ARE GOING FOR AS MUCH AS MY WHOLE APARTMENT!!!

BECAUSE OF THESE FACTORS I HAVE A VERY GOOD PRICING AND YOU CAN'T BEET THE LOCATION!!! IT'S RIGHT ON TIME SQUARE, CLOSE TO PRETTY MUCH EVERYTHING!!!! 

JUST THE NAME A FEW!!!!
- Times Square, 3 min walking 
- Theater District, 2 min walking 
- Shake Shack, 1 min walking 
- Rockefeller Center, 10 min walking 
- Restaurant row 3 min walking 
- Central Park, 10-15 min walking 
- Starbucks, 5 min walking 
-  My place is just steps away from the amazing restaurants, bars, and clubs! 

You’ll love my place because of the neighborhood/location, the comfy bed, the ambiance, the light and the roof-top and the PRICE ;)

- I ALSO HAVE A BUSINESS PARTNER WHO WILL TRY TO ACCOMMODATE YOU FOR YOR CHECK IN! 
ADITON TO THAT I HAVE AN EASY ACCESS TO THE APARTMENT AND I WILL PROVIDE YOU WITH INFORMATION HOW TO ACCESS  IN CASE THAT I OR MY PARTNER CAN'T BE THERE TO WELCOME YOU. 
I AM ALWAYS AVAILABLE TO ANSWER ANY QUESTIONS.

I am always one call/text away to accommodate any of your needs!

Just steps from the apartment!
house_rules:
• Check in time is 3PM - 2AM (next day)
• No parties or events
• Not suitable for pets
• No smoking

* No smoking of any kind is allowed in the apartment! If so please use a roof top or the front of the building! 

* You are more than welcome to enjoy yourself, however no loud music and absolutely not any ilic activities are allowed! 

* If you have more people that you initially booked please inform me! 

* Guest are welcome to stop by but not to sleep over, if they sleep over then there will be additional fee!

* If you are looking for early check in or if you have any special request please fill to contact me and most likely I will be able to help! 

* I hope that you enjoy your New York stay and that you have a great memories and stories to tell :)
